r />\n<br />\n猶疑在似即若離之間<br />\n望不穿這暖昧的眼<br />\n似是濃卻仍然很淡<br />\n天早灰藍　想告別<br />\n偏未晚"},{"pid":"0fd450d6c25885b5aae792955c8a016f31e0e606","tid":1889814,"uid":323457,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"不渴望 你不要令我多幾多渴望 <br />\n你只要為我點一點火 <br />\n然後讓我此刻至少可度過<br />\n我可以令你差不有快樂<br />\n我可以為你點一點火然後望你輪廓<br />\n不想甚麼悲壯 不想甚麼沮喪<br />\n煙圈悄悄墜落 煙灰至少將心事証明燃燒過"},{"pid":"7b3548b120cd9fec4a58cb02a165bb37164d4bd9","tid":1889814,"uid":332027,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"一早篇好的情人 早晚 始終 會等到"},{"pid":"664a36e0e655c464c272d561d2b48c699d21f88b","tid":1889814,"uid":190187,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T18:41:18.000Z","msg":"殘忍只需一棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5078df141279bc9c6ca00ed5ca701adb3e21d5","tid":1889814,"uid":555,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T18:47:14.000Z","msg":"就似夢裡面熾熱愛海變冰川"},{"pid":"e4f042535205b8c6f126fe7d3f8514fa3925537f","tid":1889814,"uid":268623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"百變小櫻魔法神奇誰可阻擋"},{"pid":"f04809c4e2216c34802f8442db26aef808bb38b8","tid":1889814,"uid":210794,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"再見不到也許紋身少不免 <br />\n但金毛ling何事秋風悲畫扇"},{"pid":"452aa3878c472fa813955d0eb6daf90daaded37a","tid":1889814,"uid":274204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:53:15.000Z","msg":"同甘苦抗疫挽手　齊心抵抗別送頭<br />\n來年摘下面罩　為著去煲底見你"},{"pid":"74c9e848ce0eed2d93d47042602c1eb4fb846a8d","tid":1889814,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"我個春袋 你個春袋<br />\n互咬先至係甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d165878065ef